---
title: Creamy Bacon, Chicken Breast and Ricotta Pasta with Parmesan and Peas
description: Inspired by the perfect Roman pasta - carbonara - this penne dish features rich bacon, hearty chicken and a silky ricotta sauce. Sweet green peas burst in each bite!
